Package com.intellij.openapi.externalSystem.model.task

Interface ExternalSystemTaskNotificationListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExternalSystemProcessingManager, ExternalSystemTaskNotificationListenerAdapter, GradleMavenProjectImportNotificationListener, GradleProjectImportNotificationListener

    public interface ExternalSystemTaskNotificationListener
    Defines contract for callback to listen external task notifications.

      • beforeCancel

        void beforeCancel(ExternalSystemTaskId id)
        Notifies that task with the given id is queued for the cancellation.

        'Queued' here means that intellij process-local codebase receives request to cancel the target task and even has not been sent it to the slave gradle api process.

        Parameters:
        id - target task's id
